article.headline: Wilson scores 16 as UL Monroe knocks off Champion Christian 110-63
article.description: — Jacob Wilson's 16 points helped UL Monroe defeat Champion Christian 110-63 on Tuesday night.
article.linkText: Wilson scores 16 as UL Monroe knocks off Champion Christian 110-63
article.story: MONROE, La. -- — Jacob Wilson's 16 points helped UL Monroe defeat Champion Christian 110-63 on Tuesday night. Wilson also added seven assists for the Warhawks (4-3). Jerry Ngopot added 14 points while finishing 7 of 8 from the floor, and they also had 10 rebounds. P.D. McCraney went 4 of 7 from the field to finish with 11 points. Xavier Hall finished with 18 points for the Tigers. Joshua Walpole added eight points for Champion Christian. In addition, Ariyon Williams finished with seven points and four assists. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
